<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #10B981; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; }
        .footer { background-color: #333; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
        .success-box { background-color: #D1FAE5; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .amount { font-size: 32px; color: #10B981; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>âœ“ Refund Processed!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{customerName}},</p>
            
            <p>Great news! Your refund has been processed successfully.</p>
            
            <div class="success-box">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; text-align: center;">Refund Amount</p>
                <p class="amount" style="text-align: center; margin: 0;">${{refundAmount}}</p>
                <hr style="margin: 20px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #10B981;">
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>RMA Number:</strong> {{rmaNumber}}</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Refund Method:</strong> {{refundMethod}}</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Processing Time:</strong> {{estimatedDays}} business days</p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
            <p>Your refund has been sent back to your original payment method. Please allow {{estimatedDays}} business days for the funds to appear in your account, depending on your bank's processing time.</p>
            
            <p>If you don't see the refund after {{estimatedDays}} business days, please check with your financial institution or contact us for assistance.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for shopping with CitadelBuy. We hope to serve you again soon!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 CitadelBuy. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
